\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô
\ip Ia nuk 60 Pol ramar…ô ia kalapus fwe taon n…ôha Rom nuk k…ôru, n…ôn…ô m…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me rukurau ia taon n…ôha Efesas. Efesas in taon asori riti. N…ô…°kiariien asori s…ôv…ôi Pol ia n…ôkuku…ô i in i m…ô n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel tuh…ôuvehe mh…ômwhen n…®pwrai i…ôrmama kuatia ia Kristo. Noien n…ôha ramesi pen n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®nam…ôrkwaf…ô ir…ô fwe kupw…ôn. Pol r…®ni m…ô s…ôuvehe mho kuatia ia Iesu Kristo, ro pen tsam…ôkeikei mhokeikei k…®taha me. Pol ramahat…ôn k…®taha m…ô tsam…ôkeikei mhar…ô ia nokeikeiien r…ômwhen ia i…ôrman rokeikei s…ôv…ônhi pran, m…®ne tata m…®ne mama krouokeikei s…ôv…ônrau i…ôkunouihi, m…®ne slef trokeikei s…ôv…ônhi i…ôm…ô asori. Pol ram…ô…°kiari mwi ia nakalasia me. R…®pko mh…ô nous…ôs…®mw…®nien …ôpa s…ôv…ônraha fwe Efesas, m…ôt…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme hahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo rukurau ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i. Pol r…®ni m…ô Iesu rokeikei k…®taha r…ômwhen k…®taha sokeikei n…®pwrataha m…®ne r…ômwhen ia i…ôrman rokeikei pran s…ôv…ônhi. Ia n…ôkuku…ô i rusipek…®n ia nakalasia me m…®ni m…ô ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia n…®pwrai Kristo, mh…ômwhen ia nimw…ô riti s…ô Kumwes…ôn rauvrh…ôk…®n, mh…ômwhen mwi ia pran s…ôv…ôi Kristo.
\c 1
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rakupw…ôn
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Rom 1:1,7, 1Kor 1:1, Kol 1:1, Wok Me 18:19-21, Wok Me 19:1\x*Iou Pol. Iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®no r…ômwhen ia s…ô in rokeikei muvehi ut…ô iou m…ô tako.
\p N…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi ia taon n…ôha Efesas k…®miaha hiamahat…ôt…ô p…ôrhien ia Iesu Kristo.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 2Kor 1:2, Kol 1:2\x*N…ôfwakiien s…ôiou m…ô Kumwes…ôn tata s…ôk…®taha m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha, trou…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha.
\s1 Kumwes…ôn r…ôkwein amasan ia k…®taha s…ôm…ôme s…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha Kristo
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Efes 2:6\x*Pw…ôh s…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni Kumwes…ôn i in Kumwes…ôn m…®ne Tata s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo. In r…®n…ôkwein amasan ia k…®taha n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme s…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha Kristo, m…ôriari pehe ia n…ôn…®mw…®taha m…®ne narimnari amasan me pam s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuku pen ia n…®t…ôt…ô ia neiai.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Jon 15:16, 17:24, 2Tes 2:13, Efes 5:27, Kol 1:22\x*In ruv…ôrfi raka k…®taha fwe tui n…ôp…®n t…®pr…ôn…ô ramiw…ôn ihi, m…ô ts…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha Kristo, n…ôn…ô mh…ôuvehe mho n…ôkur ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi, tsatukwatukw pam ia n…ônimen. T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in rokeikei k…®taha,
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Jon 1:12\x*in r…®n…ômri …ôp…ô raka k…®taha fwe tui anan, m…ô k…®taha ts…ôuvehe mho n…®pwn…ôt…®n me ia Iesu Kristo. Noien n…ôha ramesi pen n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien amasan s…ôv…ônhi m…®ne n…ôfe in rokeikei m…ô tro.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Mat 3:17, Kol 1:13\x*Kumwes…ôn ro iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ô tsam…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in t…® namasanien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ramasan m…ôpi raka. In r…ôriari pehe au…ôr a namasanien n…ôha m k…®taha sam…ôuvehi raku pen t…® T…®ni keikei.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Efes 2:7, Kol 1:14,20\x*T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha s…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha min, n…®ten r…®fi nari ia k…®taha, mo Kumwes…ôn tr…ôpw…ôh n…ôrpw…®nien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha. Noien n…ôha ramesi pen namasanien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô rasori p…®k anan.
\v 8 In r…ôt…ô…°i irapw namasanien n…ôha m k…®taha r…ôpi raka, mo k…®taha s…ôukur…ôn mh…ôt…ô sas ia narimnari me pam.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Rom 16:25\x*In ro pui pehe m k…®taha n…ôfe in r…®nam…ôrkwaf…ô i fwe kupw…ôn mokeikei m…ô tro. N…ôri n…ôha ramesi pen n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien amasan s…ôv…ônhi s…ô in tro k…®ni n…ô…°hi Kristo ir…ô.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Kal 4:4, Kol 1:16,20\x*Kumwes…ôn tro n…ôri n…ôha ia n…ôp…®n atukwatukw s…ôv…ônhi, mous…ôs…®mw…®n narimnari me pam ia neiai m…®ne ia t…®pr…ôn…ô h…ôuvehe Kristo trasori ia nir…ôha.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Rom 8:28-29\x*Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôrfi k…®maha mwi m…ô k…®maha tah…ôuvehe n…ôrmama s…ôv…ônhi, mho kuatia k…®maha Kristo. In ro iam…®nha ir…ô mesi pen n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô in ruv…ôukur…ôn raka fwe tui anan. In Kumwes…ôn s…ô ramo narimnari me pam mamesi pen n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi m…®ne n…ôfe rokeikei m…ô tro.
\v 12 N…ôn…ô in rokeikei m…ô k…®maha s…ôm…ôme iah…ôm…ôukupw…ôn mh…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®maha ia Kristo taham…ôkeikei mh…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in t…® nasoriien s…ôv…ônhi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Kol 1:4-6, Efes 4:30\x*N…ôn…ô k…®miaha mwi hi…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®miaha min n…ôp…®n hi…ôre…°i n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien, n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô Kumwes…ôn rauvehim…®ru k…®miaha ir…ô. T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®miaha hi…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Kristo, Kumwes…ôn r…ômri pen mak s…ôv…ônhi ia k…®miaha rahat…ôn pen m…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi. Mak n…ô in n…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôni m…ô truvei pehe.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt 2Kor 1:22\x*T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan ramar…ô ia k…®taha, n…ôn…ô, k…®taha s…ôukur…ôn amasan m…ô Kumwes…ôn truvei pehe pam narimnari amasan me n…ôha in r…®n…ômri karen m…ô s…ôk…®taha. K…®taha ts…ôuvehi narimnari amasan me n…ôha n…ôp…®n Kumwes…ôn tr…®fi anan nari ia k…®taha. Pw…ôh s…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in t…® nasoriien s…ôv…ônhi!
\s1 N…ôfwakiien m…®ne n…®ni viviien
\p 
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 1:15-16 \xt Kol 1:3-4, 1Tes 1:2\x*Ro pen, ia n…ôp…®n me pam iakani vivi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha, m…ôpw…ôh n…ôpw…ôhien, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakuv…ôre…°i raka kam…®ni nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha ia I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu, m…®ne nokeikeiien s…ôk…®miaha s…ô ramev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama me pam s…ôv…ônhi. Ia n…ôp…®n me pam iakani k…®miaha ia n…ôfwakiien me s…ôiou,
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Kol 1:9\x*mam…ôres Kumwes…ôn s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo, Tata s…ô ramasan p…®k, m…ô in truvei pehe N…ôn…®mw…®n s…ôv…ônhi m k…®miaha. N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha tro k…®miaha hi…ôukur…ôn nari, mo pui Kumwes…ôn m k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôukur…ôn amasan in.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Efes 4:4, Kol 1:12\x*Iakam…ôres m…ô fwe imw…ô ia rer…®miaha n…ômr…®miaha trukuraan m…ô tih…ôt…ô sas n…ôri n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôkwein k…®miaha tukwe m…®ni m…ô tih…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ir…ô. Tih…ôt…ô sas mwi ia narimnari amasan me r…®p…®k s…ôm…ôme in truvei pen m n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi,
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Kol 1:11\x*m…®ne n…®skaiien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô rasori anan ia k…®taha n…ôrmama sam…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Kristo. N…®skaiien n…ôha r…ômwhen ia n…®skaiien asori s…ôv…ônhi
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt 2Kor 13:4, Kol 2:12, Hip 1:3, Kol 1:16, 2:10\x*s…ô in r…®no Kristo ir…ô r…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi, mar…ô mo mwi in r…ôkure ia n…®karen mwatuk ia n…®t…ôt…ô ia neiai.
\v 21 Kwopun Kristo ram…ôkure ik…®n in fwe ir…ônh…ô anan m…ôpi raka pam n…ôn…®mw…®n me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuvehi nasoriien m…®ne n…ôr…®m…ônuien, m…ôpi raka pam n…ôm…ô skai me m…®ne n…ôr…®m…ônu me. R…ômwhen a mwi n…ôha…° s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen min in ir…ônh…ô anan m…ôpi raka naha…° me pam s…ôm…ôme kam…®ni. R…®pko mh…ô n…ôha…° me …ôpa i s…ôm…ôme kam…®ni ia n…ôp…®n i ipwet m…®ne m…ôt…ô n…ôha…° me n…ôha mwi s…ôm…ôme tuk…®ni ia n…ôp…®n s…ô tr…®pkuvehe.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Sam 8:6, Mat 28:18\x*Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ômri narimnari me pam kamhar…ô inh…ôr…®pw ia t…®pa…°e n…®sui Kristo n…ôn…ô mo in ruvehe masori ia narimnari me pam. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ô trasitu ia nakalasia me s…ôv…ônhi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Efes 4:10,15, Rom 12:5, Kol 1:18\x*Nakalasia me n…ôha ir…ôha n…ô n…®pwrai Kristo, Kristo ruku…ôr ia nir…ôha, n…ôn…ô ia noien a mwi n…ôha in ruku…ôr ia narimnari me pam.
\c 2
\s1 Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvehim…®ru k…®taha ia namasanien s…ôv…ônhi
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Kol 1:21, 2:13\x*Fwe kupw…ôn k…®miaha hi…ômwhen m…ô hi…ôuvamh…ô raka t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hiam…ôrui n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô mamho noien …ôr…ôha me.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Kol 3:7, Taet 3:3, Jon 12:31, Efes 5:6, 6:12\x*Fwe kupw…ôn hiamav…ôn mamho noien …ôr…ôha me n…ôha, mamhesi pen suatuk s…ôv…ôi t…®pr…ôn…ô i, mamh…ôkurir…ô i…ôremh…ô asori s…ô ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia n…ôn…®mw…®n …ôr…ôha me ia n…®ma…°oua…°ou. In n…ôha n…ôn…®mw…®n s…ô ramowok n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni ia reri n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrui n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Kol 3:6\x*Fwe kupw…ôn k…®taha pam s…ômwhen a ia nir…ôha. Noien …ôr…ôha me rer…®taha rokeikei p…®k kamh…ôiri k…®taha samo n…ôfe n…ô…°h…®n n…®pwrataha m…®ne n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha krouokeikei. Ro pen ia noien s…ôk…®taha k…®taha s…ômwhen a ia n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme hamo niemaha ram…ôpi p…®k Kumwes…ôn.
\v 4 M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn napiien s…ôv…ônhi rasori. Nokeikeiien rokeikei k…®taha ir…ô rasori p…®k anan,
\v 5 mo in ruvei pehe n…®m…®ruien m k…®taha n…ôp…®n s…ômwhen ia n…ôrmama h…ôuvamh…ô raka ia noien …ôr…ôha me, s…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien k…®taha Kristo. (Kumwes…ôn r…®nasitu ia k…®miaha ia namasanien s…ôv…ônhi n…ôn…ô muvehim…®ru k…®miaha.)
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Kol 2:12\x*N…ôn…ô ia noien n…ôha s…ô Kumwes…ôn ro k…®taha s…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha Iesu Kristo, in ruvehi ut…ô k…®taha min, s…ôkure k…®taha min ia n…®t…ôt…ô ia neiai.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Efes 1:7\x*In rokeikei m…ô ia n…ôp…®n me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuvehe in trukur…ôn noien n…ôrmama h…ôtoni namasanien i s…ôv…ônhi rasori p…®k anan irau nokeikeiien krauvehe tukutaha ia Iesu Kristo.
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Jon 4:10, Hip 6:4\x*Kumwes…ôn r…®nasitu ia k…®miaha ia namasanien s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô muvehim…®ru k…®miaha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hiam…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Kristo. Narimnari me n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô k…®miaha atukw hi…ôno, m…ôt…ô r…ômwhen ia nari riti s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pehe au…ôr a m k…®miaha.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1Kor 1:29-31, 2Tim 1:9\x*Ro pen ko i…ôrmama riti r…®pk…ôfi…ôut…ô atukw mh…ô in tukwe, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô r…®pko mh…ô k…®miaha hi…ôno narimnari me n…ôha.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Taet 2:14\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha n…ôrmama Kumwes…ôn r…®no wok ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®taha, mo k…®taha s…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha Iesu Kristo m…ô k…®taha tsamo noien amasan me. Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôpn…ôpen…ô raka ia noien amasan me n…ôha fwe kupw…ôn m…ô k…®taha tsamar…ô mamho.
\s1 N…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Efes 5:8\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô k…®miaha n…ôkur Isrel ia n…®pwramiaha rer…®miaha tramrhi nar…ôien kupw…ôn s…ôk…®miaha. N…ôkur Isrel kam…®ni ir…ôha m…ô n…ôrmama kauvehi ninhum m…®nraha ir…ôha kamh…ôni …ôr…ôha k…®miaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®pkuvehi mh…ô ninhum m k…®miaha. Nuvehiien ninhum n…ôha iakani kamo ia n…®pwrai i…ôrmama, n…ôrmama kamho ia r…ô…°…®nraha.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Kol 1:21, Rom 9:4, 1Tes 4:13\x*K…®miaha rer…®miaha tramrhi m…ô fwe kupw…ôn k…®miaha hiamar…ô Kristo riw…ôn tukumiaha, k…®miaha n…ôkur iru…ô me, r…®pko mh…ô k…®miaha n…ôkur Isrel, k…®miaha n…ôkur pw…®spw…®s me, ko hi…ôpkuvehi mh…ô narimnari me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes fwe kupw…ôn m…ô truvei pen m n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi. Fwe kupw…ôn nar…ôien s…ôk…®miaha ia t…ôkure t…®pr…ôn…ô i nari amasan riti riw…ôn ir…ô s…ô tihameitenhi m…ô truvehe, n…ôn…ô hi…ôreirei anan Kumwes…ôn.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Kol 1:20\x*Fwe kupw…ôn k…®miaha hiam…ôuv…ôn isipw…®n t…® Kumwes…ôn, m…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni hiam…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®miaha Iesu Kristo, n…ôn…ô mh…ôuvehe ipaka t…® Kumwes…ôn ia n…®te Kristo.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Aes 9:6, 1Kor 12:13, Kol 2:14\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kristo in n…ô n…ôm…ôrinuien s…ôk…®taha in r…®no k…®taha n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne s…ôm…ôme r…®pko mh…ô k…®taha n…ôkur Isrel s…ôuvehe mho kuatia. N…ôpai k…®no ia k…ôru…ôterei s…ô fwe kupw…ôn ro k…®taha sam…ômw…ôki k…®taha me, r…ôrp…®fi k…®taha s…ôpkuvehe mh…ô mho kuatia, Kristo r…®nousi …ôtestesi n…ôpai n…ôha r…®mwei ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 2Kor 5:17, Kol 1:20,22\x*In ruvehi raka Loa s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel ir…ôha natuak…ômien me ir…ô, m…ô in rukur…ôn nuvi s…®mw…®nien ia n…®pwran n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel krouvehe i…ôrmama vi riti ia nirau. Ia noien n…ôha in r…ômri n…ôm…ôrinuien.
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Sek 9:10\x*Ia nei kamarkuaui in rous…ôs…®mw…®n k…®taha p…ôri ia n…®pwran kuatia, m…®peki k…®taha s…ôuvehe t…® Kumwes…ôn, mousi …ôpune noien i sam…ômw…ôki k…®taha me.
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Aes 57:19\x*In r…®m…ôuvehe m…ôvisau n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi n…ôm…ôrinuien rev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama isipw…®n t…® Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô m…ôvisau mwi n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha rev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama ipaka tukwe.
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Efes 3:12\x*N…ôn…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha s…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha min, k…®taha n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne s…ôm…ôme r…®pko mh…ô k…®taha n…ôkur Isrel k…®taha pam s…ôukur…ôn nuvnimw…ôien ia N…ôn…®mw…®n kuatia mh…ôuv…ôn t…® Tata Kumwes…ôn.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Efes 3:6, Hip 12:22-23\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô r…®pko mh…ô k…®miaha n…ôkur iru…ô me r…ômwhen s…ô fwe kupw…ôn, r…®pko mh…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama pw…®spw…®s me, m…ôt…ô k…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôuvehe mh…ôno kuatia k…®miaha n…ôrmama ikinan me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, k…®miaha n…ôrmama ia n…ôkwai nimw…ô s…ôv…ônhi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Mat 16:18, 1Kor 3:11\x*Kuvrh…ôk…®n nimw…ô n…ôha ia t…ôkure n…ôri s…ô aposol me m…®ne profet me h…ôn…ômri irapw. Iesu Kristo in r…ômwhen ia k…ôru…ôterei n…ôha kukupw…ôn kukurei pen ia kona kostat kuvrh…ôk…®n nimw…ô ir…ô.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Efes 4:15-16, Kol 2:19, 1Kor 3:16\x*In ram…ôkwt…ômhiri pam nimw…ô n…ôha, mamo nimw…ô n…ôha raut…ô muvehe mo nimw…ô ikinan ir…ô s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu.
